;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 V-League 2018, HLV Marian Mihail b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. L\u00fd do \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &quot;ph\u00e1 r\u00e0o&quot; l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn HLV Mihail c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV moi cua FLC Thanh Hoa van chua lo dien sau su ra di cua ong Marian Mihail.\" title=\"HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Marian Mihail.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/sau-marian-mihail-ai-se-tro-thanh-hlv-moi-cua-flc-thanh-hoa.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Marian Mihail.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n n\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5. V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u01b0a l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-tu-chuc-sau-that-bai-thu-2-o-vleague-168-183607.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Mihail Marian</span></span>, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng, L\u00ea Hu\u1ef3nh \u0110\u1ee9c hay Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng,... Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u1ed9i c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft duy\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o n\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, c\u00f2n BL\u0110 s\u1ebd s\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ngo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong hai m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua hai \u0111\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ngo\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng Ljupko Petrovic v\u00e0 Marian Mihail. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau b\u1ed1n v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 7 trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/bang-xep-hang-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018</span></span>, k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/he-lo-ly-do-thuc-su-khien-hlv-mihail-chia-tay-flc-thanh-hoa-168-183741.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn HLV Mihail chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mihail-che-hoc-tro-sau-that-bai-truoc-khanh-hoa-168-183602.html\">HLV Mihail ch\u00ea h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-khanh-hoa-vs-thanh-hoa-17h00-ngay-54-vleague-2018-372-183572.html\">Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 3-1 Thanh H\u00f3a (KT): B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee9u n\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-linh-an-phat-cua-ldbd-chau-a-168-183450.html\">CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u0129nh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/chum-anh-co-dong-vien-doi-ao-36-va-37-trong-tran-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-291-183330.html\">Ch\u00f9m \u1ea3nh: C\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o 36 v\u00e0 37 trong tr\u1eadn derby B\u1eafc Trung B\u1ed9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/guc-nga-truoc-thanh-hoa-hlv-slna-do-loi-cho-ong-park-hang-seo-168-183329.html\">G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, HLV SLNA \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1027","checkdouble":"183998"},{"date":"07:49 11/04","title":"L\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch, sao Roma ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i n\u1ed7i \u0111au Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/lam-nen-ky-tich-sao-roma-tien-the-xat-muoi-noi-dau-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContain