<td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguoi hung Dzeko noi gi sau cuoc loi nguoc dong Roma 3-0 Barca hinh anh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Dzeko n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng Roma 3-0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/lam-nen-ky-tich-sao-roma-tien-the-xat-muoi-noi-dau-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dzeko t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn Roma 3-0 Barca t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Dzeko x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u1edfi anh c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00edu gi\u1eef hy v\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Camp Nou c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Man City sau tr\u1eadn Roma 3-0 Barca:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Barcelona thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1edd Roma \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 l\u00ean h\u1ecd ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. Th\u1eafng tr\u1eafng Barca ba b\u00e0n v\u00e0 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 Roma c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Kh\u00f4ng ai tin ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Barca v\u00e0 gi\u1edd th\u00ec sao? T\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Champions League.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Roma c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; Dzeko g\u1ee3i l\u1ea1i cho Chelsea th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua h\u1ee5t anh h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng Alvaro Morata hay Olivier Giroud.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Barca, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGia Khoa &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1026","checkdouble":"183987"},{"date":"07:47 11/04","title":"Sergio Busquets th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Barca x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thua Roma","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/sergio-busquets-thua-nhan-barca-xung-dang-thua-roma.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72