r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Sergio Busquets th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Barca thua x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roma, Barca c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 57% nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n, trong \u0111\u00f3 3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, qu\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh con s\u1ed1 17 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 6 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Busquets phat bieu ve tran Roma vs Barca hinh anh\" title=\"Sergio Busquets ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/sergio-busquets-thua-nhan-barca-xung-dang-thua-roma.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Busquets chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, Barca \u0111\u1ec3 Roma ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 3 l\u1ea7n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-roma-vs-barca-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183967.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Roma vs Barca</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergio Busquets ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp;n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Barca l\u1ea1i thua 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 hay. H\u1ecd l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Tinh th\u1ea7n, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Barca x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thua tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Busquets n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca, sau \u0111\u00f3 HLV Ernesto Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Thua theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Roma \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iniesta Barca 3-0 Roma\" title=\"Iniesta Barca 3-0 Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/huyen-thoai-barca-vinh-vien-chia-tay-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iniesta kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Andres Iniesta th\u1eadm th\u00ec cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barca trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma 3-0 Barca<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Roma 3-0 Barca\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma 3-0 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Thong-so-Roma-3-0-Barca.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma 3-0 Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1025","checkdouble":"183988"},{"date":"08:06 11/04","title":"Mane: \"Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/mane-liverpool-co-the-danh-bai-bat-ky-doi-bong-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adCon