   <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sadio Mane noi ve tran Man City vs Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"Sadio Mane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Sadio-Mane-noi-ve-tran-Man-City-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City 2-1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00e0nh cho Man City, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. Liverpool tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd gi\u00fap The Kop ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-man-city-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183969.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City vs Liverpool </strong></span>\u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp hi\u00ean ngang ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ma xanh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 tin 5-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mane th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane phat bieu ve tran Man City vs Liverpool\" title=\"Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/mane-liverpool-co-the-danh-bai-bat-ky-doi-bong-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4&nbsp;\u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 ai c\u1ea3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, b\u1edfi v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp; Man City vs Liverpool, anh d\u00e0nh cho HLV Klopp nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1024","checkdouble":"183989"},{"date":"08:09 11/04","title":"Gabriel Jesus: \"Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng...\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/gabriel-jesus-man-city-da-khoi-dau-tot-nhung.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absol