align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gabriel Jesus phat bieu ve tran Man City vs Liverpool\" title=\"Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/gabriel-jesus-man-city-da-khoi-dau-tot-nhung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t khi th\u0103ng hoa h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u. Liverpool l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi khi\u1ebfn Man City thua tr\u1eadn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Gabriel Jesus cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Man City thua tr\u1eadn th\u00ec Pep l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Man xanh thua v\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/bi-loai-xung-dang-khoi-c1-pep-van-trut-gian-len-trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Sane l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn. Ch\u00ednh t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u1ebfu pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb may m\u1eafn, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Man City kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thua tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1023","checkdouble":"183996"},{"date":"09:00 11/04","title":"Real Madrid vs Juventus (01h45 ng\u00e0y 12/4): C\u1ecdp ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 da","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-vid