Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Buffon v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 ngay sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, khi B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Juve thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, t\u1eeb ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1eabn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t CLB Italia h\u01a1n, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0&hellip; t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Paulo Dybala.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 v\u00e0 ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p. Nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Max Allegri \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh bong da 24h Real Madrid vs Juventus tu ket Cup C1 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h Real Madrid vs Juventus t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-ngay-hom-nay-1142018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-khien-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-khi-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-juve-184-183489.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cris Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u00e1t cu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n</span>. Ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 bay trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u1ea5y, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 cao tr\u00ean 2m so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00ednh trong 15 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ghi &ldquo;v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n&rdquo;&hellip; 25 b\u00e0n. M\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, CR7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Madrid. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zidane \u0111\u01b0a ra ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juve (khi \u0111\u00f3 Real \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1). B\u1edfi v\u1eady x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c anh th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua Tottenham t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n PSG \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp hay kh\u00f4ng, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd (ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c) ghi bao nhi\u00eau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n, cho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 &ldquo;c\u1ee9ng&rdquo; nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sieu pham nga ban den cua Ronaldo\" title=\"Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/qua-bat-luc-truoc-doi-thu-buffon-so-sanh-ronaldo-voi-vua-bong-da.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1eddi chia tay c\u1ee7a Buffon</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi gi\u1eefa tr\u01b0a c\u1ee7a CR7, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Gianluigi Buffon \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Italia m\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n&hellip; ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quay l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1ee1ng 40 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/buffon-noi-gi-khi-bi-coi-la-can-duong-the-he-tre-439-182679.html\" target=\"_blank\">Buffon h\u1ebft th\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 &ldquo;ch\u00e0y c\u1ed1i&rdquo; c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Juve, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong khung g\u1ed7. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Buffon \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n x\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u. Li\u1ec7u anh c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Gigi t\u1ea1i Champions League, khi Juventus g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha &ldquo;l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c&rdquo;. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 4 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng &ldquo;h\u1ee9ng ch\u00ed&rdquo; l\u00e0m \u0111\u00f4i ba b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa 2 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, Juve c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o. Ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;d\u00ednh th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-vs-real-khi-messi-moi-qua-nho-be-so-voi-cr7-184-183488.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 so v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon vs Ronaldo\" title=\"Buffon vs Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i \u0111au \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Buffon, khi anh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Bernabeu v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Ronaldo s\u1ebd coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ecdp ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 da, d\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 t\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, trong 18/22 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 12/15 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ronaldo ghi 25 b\u00e0n trong 15 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 9 b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Juve.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trong 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i &ndash; l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1), Juve \u0111\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trong 22 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, Real Madrid th\u1eafng 10, Juventus th\u1eafng 8 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Sergio Ramos s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Vallejo v\u00e0 Nacho b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Bentacur (nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng) v\u00e0 Dybala (\u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf) c\u0169ng ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Barzagli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Juventus \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Benatia v\u00e0 Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Real Madrid vs Juventus\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Real Madrid vs Juventus<br>\r\n</strong> <span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088661/003100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real Madrid vs Juventus<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Real Madrid vs Juventus:</strong> 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u0