r\n- Chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Roma t\u1eeb khi tham d\u1ef1 c\u00fap C1/ Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Barca nh\u1eadn 3 b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Champions League c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung thong ke dang nho sau tran dau Roma vs Barca hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Barca-bat-luc-truoc-lao-tuong-nhu-Dzeko.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n- <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-roma-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183963.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca thua Roma 0-3</strong></span> v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 5 (thua 4, h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong 5 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, Blaugrana ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sau khi th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1</strong></span>, Edin Dzeko \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n sau 3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Barca, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Dzeko c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Champions League, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m 2009 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Wolfsburg.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Daniele De Rossi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Champions League k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2015 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayer Leverkusen).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roma tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Champions League \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out sau khi thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, sau Deportivo m\u00f9a 2003/04 v\u00e0 Barca m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00fap C1, Barca c\u0169ng m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Barca nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Roma, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Roma 3-0 Barca\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn 