h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1ea7n t\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn thua Man City 1-2 Liverpool l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 sau th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i Champions League 2017/18 trong th\u1ebf c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vi sao Guardiola bi duoi len khan dai tran Man City 1-2 Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"V\u00ec sao Guardiola b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/bi-loai-xung-dang-khoi-c1-pep-van-trut-gian-len-trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Pep Guardiola c\u00f3 l\u00fd do b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool v\u00e0 n\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Leroy Sane, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t oan u\u1ed5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb HLV x\u1ee9 Catalonia sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool: \u201cT\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 khi c\u00f9ng \u0111i v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m k\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u00f4ng ta \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m n\u00e0o c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb pha ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Salah trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn, v\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Liverpool v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng ta t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\">Tranh c\u00e3i tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool: Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb hay ch\u01b0a?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool trong s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1020","checkdouble":"183980"},{"date":"06:33 11/04","title":"Bayern Munich vs Sevilla (01h45 ng\u00e0y 12/04): S\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/Preview-Bayern-Munich-vs-Sevilla.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;borde