der-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern Munich vs Sevilla \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Song c\u00fa s\u1ed1c mang t\u00ean&nbsp;Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 Sevilla hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo;.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-sevilla-vs-bayern-munich-01h45-ngay-44-champions-league-201718-372-183464.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa Sevilla v\u00e0 Bayern</strong></span>, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Henyckes v\u1eabn ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng (58%) v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (14 so v\u1edbi 9). &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich vs Sevilla - Tu ket luot ve Champions League hinh anh\" title=\"Bayern Munich vs Sevilla - T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Bayern-Munich-vs-Sevilla---Tu-ket-luot-ve-Champions-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla 2-1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Jesus Navas v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thiago Alcantara gi\u00fap Bayern Munich chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed thua 0-1 v\u1eabn ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJupp Henyckes l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 12 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Champions League, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Sevilla tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Augsburg v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-duc/augsburg-14-bayern-munich-hum-xam-chinh-thuc-dang-quang-193-183757.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jupp Heynckes ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga</strong></span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp H\u00f9m x\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u1edf Bundesliga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t, Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Champions League.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" title=\"Preview Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Preview-Bayern-Munich-vs-Sevilla.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich vs Sevilla \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern Munich vs Sevilla, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp song v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c theo c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ebfn 12 b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Allianz Arena, Hamburg v\u00e0 Dortmund ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jupp Henyckes c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 14 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n thua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Bayern s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Manuel Neuer, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kingsley Coman, David Alaba, Arturo Vidal l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sevilla v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb AS Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong kho\u1ea3ng 35 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu Pablo Sarabia ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh khi phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla dut mach bat bai truoc cac doi bong Duc tren san nha\" title=\"Sevilla \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/sevilla-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sevilla ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nThua 1-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Vincenzo Montella \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Sevilla bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/bayern-munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Bayern Munich</strong></span> l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Sevilla c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u1ede Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a La Liga ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool. Trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Anfield Sevilla c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Montella th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i M.U 2-1 ngay t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Manolas ghi ban quyet dinh cho Roma 3-0 Barca\" title=\"Manolas ghi ban quyet dinh cho Roma 3-0 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Manolas-ghi-ban-quyet-dinh-cho-Roma-3-0-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd gi\u00fap Sevilla hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n2 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Champions League, Sevilla \u0111\u1ec1u ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Bayern.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Montella \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Celta Vigo cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSevilla d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-4 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Allianz Arena.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t Miguel Layun, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Kjaer, Mercado v\u00e0 Corchia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. C\u00fa s\u1ed1c mang t\u00ean Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 Sevilla hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div><strong>Bayern Munich (4-1-4-1): </strong>26.Ulreich; 32.Kimmich, 17.Boateng, 5.Hummels, 13.Rafinha; 8.Martinez; 25.Muller, 6.Thiago, 11.James Rodriguez, 7.Ribery; 9.Lewandowski</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>Sevilla (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Rico; 16.Navas, 6.Carrico, 5.Lenglet, 18.Escudero; 15.N'Zonzi, 10.Banega; 17.Sarabia, 22.Vazquez, 11.Correa; 20.Muriel</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 3-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1019","checkdouble":"183982"},{"date":"06:05 11/04","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerela