8px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Olimpico \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona. HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u1edbi AS Roma. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 1 tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 4-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Cho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ngh\u0129 90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i Olimpico ch\u1ec9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 6 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Edin Dzeko. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a Giallorossi. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0 sang hi\u1ec7p 2, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Daniele De Rossi v\u00e0 Kostas Manolas l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ghi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde phat bieu sau tran Roma vs Barca hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/HLV-Valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Roma-vs-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, d\u00f9 t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 4-4 nh\u01b0ng Roma l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League b\u1edfi lu\u1eadt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. D\u00f9 thua 1-4 t\u1ea1i Camp Nou song <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>m\u00e0n Roma h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Barca 3-0</strong></span> t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Eusebio Di Francesco ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nValverde th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 n\u00e0y. Theo \u00f4ng, Roma c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Di Francesco \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. \u201cKhi b\u1ea1n thua cu\u1ed9c theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cao trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng b\u00f3ng 2 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-roma-vs-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\