 kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho l\u1edbp tr\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"denis suarez\" title=\"denis suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/18/barca-mat-gan-1-trieu-euro-neu-denis-suarez-da-tran-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><em>Messi k\u00ec v\u1ecdng Denis Suarez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Iniesta trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</em></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean vi\u1ec7c Iniesta chia tay Barca c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Valverde c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1984 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho BL\u0110 Blaugrana. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Messi \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Carles Alena.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng khi m\u00e0 Denis Suarez c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, c\u00f2n Carles \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i B.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Barca. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Carles Alena n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thay Iniesta l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Arthur \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Brazil. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft Barca \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i Gremio tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n non kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1016","checkdouble":"183973"},{"date":"22:32 10/04","title":"Hazard: \"B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League t\u1ed1t cho Chelsea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/hazard-bi-loai-khoi-champions-league-tot-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;mar