.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec1u x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao Phap khang dinh Martial muon roi MU trong he toi hinh anh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Bao-Phap-khang-dinh-Martial-muon-roi-MU-trong-he-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><em>B\u00e1o Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi</em></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial gia nh\u1eadp CLB Man United v\u00e0o m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015 t\u1eeb AS Monaco, v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ban \u0111\u1ea7u 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Old Trafford.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Anthony Martial m\u1edbi c\u00f3 27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111a s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang nung n\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi M.U sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U ngay sau m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 Mohamed Bouhafsi cho hay Martial \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alexis Sanchez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng \u00edt d\u1ea7n \u0111i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Martial \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean BL\u0110 M.U b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00eca gi\u1ea3i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t cho anh khi m\u00e0 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u1eadn k\u1ec1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anthony Martial, Philippe Lamboley c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi 5 n\u0103m t\u1eeb Man Utd. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1014","checkdouble":"183971"},{"date":"23:18 10/04","title":"Mourinho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tay Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/mourinho-muon-tay-pogba-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-nay-trong-he-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer